State and Main;;2000;;R;;Comedy,Drama;;6.8;;David Mamet;;Philip Seymour Hoffman,William H. Macy,Rebecca Pidgeon,Michael Higgins,Michael Bradshaw,Morris Lamore,Allen Soule,Clark Gregg,Ricky Jay,Julia Stiles,Matt Malloy,Charles Durning,Tony V.,Tony Mamet,Jack Wallace,Michael James O'Boyle,Charlotte Potok,Christopher Kaldor;;Having left New Hampshire over excessive demands by the locals, the cast and crew of "The Old Mill" moves their movie shoot to a small town in Vermont. However, they soon discover that The Old Mill burned down in 1960, the star can't keep his pants zipped, the starlet won't take her top off, and the locals aren't quite as easily conned as they appear.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120202/